12px"><td width="198" valign="top" style="width: 198px;border-right-color: windowtext;border-bottom-color: windowtext;border-left-color: windowtext;border-right-width: 1px;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-left-width: 1px;border-top-style: none;padding: 0 7px;height: 212px"><p><span style="font-family:宋体">软件需求分析与设计实践</span></p></td><td width="284" valign="top" style="width: 284px;border-top-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-bottom-color: windowtext;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-right-color: windowtext;border-right-width: 1px;padding: 0 7px;height: 212px"><p><span style="font-family:宋体">根据课程作业要求编写《需求分析与设计项目计划》</span> &nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">实践需求工程的各个过程：需求识别、需求分析与设计</span></p><p><span>OOA</span><span style="font-family:宋体">方法，</span><span>UML</span><span style="font-family:宋体">描述</span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体">需求定义：软件需求说明文档、需求管理：变更的控制与跟踪记录报告</span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体">采用</span><span>UML</span><span style="font-family:宋体">方法，完成基本的软件概要设计说明书</span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体">提出改进措施：技术方法的改进，软件需求分析及设计过程的改进建议</span></p></td><td width="71" valign="top" style="width: 71px;border-top-style: none;border-left-style: none;border-bottom-color: windowtext;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-right-color: windowtext;border-right-width: 1px;padding: 0 7px;height: 212px"><p><span>6</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体">（二）</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-family:宋体">考试评分与建议</span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体">以大型课程作业的方式，采用项目管理的方法，对具体课程作业内容项目：对“软件工程教学辅助系统”项目的需求进行分析与设计。</span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体">课程作业要求：</span></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:28px"><span>1.<span style="font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">每</span><span>5-8</span><span style="font-family:宋体">人组成一个项目小组，在项目经理（组长）的领导下，团结协作共同完成课程作业。</span></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:28px"><span>2.<span style="font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">提供的《需求分析与设计项目计划》</span></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:28px"><span>3.<span style="font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">实践需求工程的各个过程，主要包括：</span></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:56px"><span>a.<span style="font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">需求识别：教师、学生、技术专家等需求</span></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:56px"><span>b.<span style="font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">重点完成需求分析与设计：</span><span>OOA</span><span style="font-family:宋体">方法，</span><span>UML</span><span style="font-family:宋体">描述</span></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:56px"><span>c.<span style="font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">需求定义：软件需求说明文档</span></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:56px"><span>d.<span style="font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">需求的确认：需求评审会议及报告，需求基准</span><span>SRS</span></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:56px"><span>e.<span style="font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">需求管理：变更的控制与跟踪记录报告</span></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:28px"><span>4.<span style="font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">采用</span><span>UML</span><span style="font-family:宋体">方法，完成基本的软件概要设计说明书</span></p><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left:28px"><span>5.<span style="font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family:宋体">提出改进措施：</span></p><p><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="font-family:宋体">技术方法的改进，软件需求分析及设计过程的改进建议</span></p><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体">考核方式</span><span>:</span></p><p><span style="font-family:宋体">按照课程作业的三个里程碑分别进行讲评，最后每组准备</span><span>10</span><span style="font-family:宋体">分钟</span><span>PPT</span><span style="font-family:宋体">进行讲解，由全部小组的组长对其进行评审、打分，去掉最高和最低分，取平均分数占总分的</span><span>80%</span><span style="font-family:宋体">，教师综合平时情况给出的分数占</span><span>20%</span><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></p>', '<table border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="615" style="border: none"><tbody><tr><td width="47" valign="top" style="width: 47px;border-color: windowtext;border-width: 1px;padding: 0 7px"><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:宋体">学期</span></p></td><td width="57" valign="top" style="width: 57px;border-top-color: windowtext;border-right-color: windowtext;border-bottom-color: windowtext;border-top-width: 1px;border-right-width: 1px;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-left-style: none;padding: 0 7px"><p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:宋体">教学周</span></p></td><td width="180" valign="top" style="width: 180px;border-top-color: windowtext;border-right-color: windowtext;border-bottom-color: windowtext;border-top-width: 1px;border-right-width: 1px;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-left-style: none;padding: 0 7px"><